long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It just takes a click to secure your cashback. Make a purchase at any of our listed Merchant stores and you can earn up to 30% cashback!

The following are some of the advantages of adding the Insum Tap n save to your browser:

* From Ted Baker and Hush Puppies to Clarks and Booking.com, Insum has something for everyone.

* On Google search result pages, it highlights stores that provide cashback.

* It will remind you to activate your cashback before you make a purchase, saving you up to 30%.

* Withdraw to your PayPal.

* It's simple to set up and free to install.
